data.description: Welcome to this beautifully maintained 3 bed, 2 bathroom home with a spacious bonus loft, updated carpet, paint, and bathrooms. Located on a quiet cul de sac. Low maintenance functional yard features a small shop and shed both with electricty, not to mention a gas heated jacuzzi covered by a gazebo including its own video projector, screen, and sound system. Within minutes of Maricopa school district (grades K-12)  and the park. Less than 2 hours from Los Angeles, 1 hour 20 mins from the beach, 45 mins from Bakersfield, 9 mins from Taft. Don't miss out on the opportunity to own this wonderful home.
